{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198696, "create_time": 1654781256, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "难道不是葛底斯堡演说更令人叹服？试问当今……", "timestamp": 1654781256}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198703, "create_time": 1654781461, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "江总靠着一手葛底斯堡演说打遍天下。", "timestamp": 1654781461}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198709, "create_time": 1654781576, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "水平确实高 英语背诵葛底斯堡演说 技惊四座 ", "timestamp": 1654781576}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198711, "create_time": 1654781636, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 不 人家俄语 日语 都还可以 确实在外交上具有优势 能够融入西方圈子", "timestamp": 1654781636}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198715, "create_time": 1654781763, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "要是今天简简单单禁评一下🤭🤭", "timestamp": 1654781763}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198737, "create_time": 1654782676, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "我一直是亲自写稿，亲自演讲。我一口气背两百篇葛底斯堡演讲，我不换气的", "timestamp": 1654782676}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198757, "create_time": 1654783043, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "印象最深的就是江主席英语日语成绩比微积分高🤗", "timestamp": 1654783043}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198770, "create_time": 1654783317, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "然而沙叶新回忆说：\n我发言中还举了江1987年在上海交大处理学潮之事为例。那次他以一个学生运动的前辈来开导大家，起先还很受听，当江用英语背诵林肯的《葛底斯堡演说》时，有点炫示，发音也欠准，被台下一个学生“嘘”了几声，江便“尊容失色”，指着台下质问：“谁？你上来，上来！”没想到该生堂而皇之地上来了。江连声问，“你叫什么名字！”该生也坦然回答，反而使江下不了台。 \n \n我对江说：“起先你很潇洒，后来你失态了，表现的不是一个政治家的风度，而是一个父母官的架势。什么原因？就是不习惯民主。” \n \n江对我的话非但不以为忤，反倒说：“还是你们作家懂得人心，看得准。”出我意外。 ", "timestamp": 1654783317}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198782, "create_time": 1654783648, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Grace: 如果这是真的，能承认自己的错误，那我更佩服了", "timestamp": 1654783648}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 198937, "create_time": 1654786128, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Alice: 确实，比某个因为一本小黄书就毁掉一座城市的小学博士不知道高到哪里去了", "timestamp": 1654786128}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199066, "create_time": 1654788588, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Grace: 因为小黄书毁掉一座城市是啥时候的事（单纯好奇）", "timestamp": 1654788588}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199093, "create_time": 1654788943, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Isabella: 铜锣湾书店事件 https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hans/%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E5%8F%8A%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6", "timestamp": 1654788943}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199112, "create_time": 1654789205, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Isabella: 大概是香港铜锣湾书店之前经常喜欢出版一些中共领导人“秘史”，在前朝大家也就看个乐呵，没那他怎样。某人上来后，书店计划出一本《习近平的情人》。之后书店的几个员工就被绑架到了大陆。最离谱的是书店股东桂敏海，已经是瑞典国籍了，还是被在大陆判刑了，瑞典国对此表示抗议:\"你们不能这样搞我的国民\"，强国回应到：“没事，我们已经帮他自愿恢复中国国籍了”", "timestamp": 1654789205}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199120, "create_time": 1654789276, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Isabella: 港人普遍认为此事件是逃犯条例修订的根本原因", "timestamp": 1654789276}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199128, "create_time": 1654789328, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Isabella: 可以认为这是近几年来香港乱象的开端", "timestamp": 1654789328}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199164, "create_time": 1654789806, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Grace: 原来反送中是因为这事……", "timestamp": 1654789806}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 201330, "create_time": 1654847648, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Grace: 这真的是天大的笑话。。。只能希望台不被统一了", "timestamp": 1654847648}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 204427, "create_time": 1654926393, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "还有一幕不得不提，李波接受中央电视台采访，说自己“自愿偷渡回内地协助调查”", "timestamp": 1654926393}], "create_time": 1654780962, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1654926393, "likenum": 21, "n_attentions": 21, "n_comments": 18, "pid": 61764, "poll": null, "reply": 18, "text": "12月18日,示威蔓延到上海,江泽民市长出现在大批学生面前。他一开口讲话就有学生发出质问,还有些学生根本不把他放在眼里。于是他停下讲话,请学生中间的一些人上台陈述自己的观点。学生讲出自己的观点后,江泽民说,同学们对西方和中国的差别缺乏足够了解,你们对西方民主的了解都是通过翻译过来的东西,你们应当直接从外文材料去更多地了解民主。然后他用英语背诵了一段林肯的葛底斯堡演说,这让很多学生大为折服。此后几天,由于学生们忙于期末考试,同时上海市政府宣怖任何示威都要事先得到批准,学生游行也随之结束,没有发生任何意外。\n\n上海学生属实拉了", "timestamp": 1654780962}}